message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with sound rendering and spatial audio. Other likely categories could be cs.GR (graphics) as the paper discusses ray-tracing-based sound propagation, cs.MM (multimedia) as it deals with audio rendering, cs.SY (systems and control) as it discusses a new sound rendering pipeline, and cs.CV (computer vision) as it uses a unified spherical harmonic representation of directional sound.
